 trees in your wake as you move for 3 seconds. These trees last up to 15 seconds.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n 20'),(231,'Wraith Band','Shops: Main Shop Categories: Common\nPassive Effect\nRecipe Cost: 210  Total Cost: 510','https://www.dotafire.com/images/item/wraith-band.png','Wraith Band\n+3 Strength\n+6 Agility\n+3 Intelligence\n+5 Attack Speed\nAdditional Information\nA circlet with faint whispers echoing about it.'),(232,'Yasha','Shops: Main Shop Categories: Artifacts\nPassive Effect\nRecipe Cost: 600  Total Cost: 2050','https://www.dotafire.com/images/item/yasha.png','Yasha\nBonus:\n+16 Agility\n+12 Attack Speed\n+20 Movement Speed\nAdditional Information\nYasha is regarded as the swiftest weapon ever created.'),(233,'Yasha and Kaya','Shops: Main Shop\nPassive Effect\nTotal Cost: 4100','https://www.dotafire.com/images/item/yasha-and-kaya.png','Yasha and Kaya\nBonus:\n+16 Intelligence\n+16 Agility\n+16 Attack Speed\n+30 Movement Speed\n+18% Mana Loss Reduction\n+14% Spell Amplification'),(243,'Abyssal Blade','Shops: Main Shop Categories: Weapons\nActive Effect, Passive Effect\nRecipe Cost: 1750  Total Cost: 6625','https://www.dotafire.com/images/item/abyssal-blade.png','Abyssal Blade\nBonus:\n+10 Strength\n+25 Damage\n+250 Health\n+10 HP Regeneration\n\nPassive: Damage Block - 50% chance to block 70/35 damage for melee/ranged wielders\n\nActive: Blink Strike - Blinks on the target enemy.\n\nCast Range: 600\n\nActive: Overwhelm - Stun a target enemy unit for 2 seconds. Goes through Spell Immunity.\n\nCast Range: 140\nStun Duration: 2\n\n\n\n\n 35\n\n\n\n\n\n 75\n\n\n\n\n\nPassive: Bash - Gives a chance to stun for 1.5 seconds.\n\nProc Chance (Melee): 25%\nProc Chance (Ranged): 10%\nStun Duration: 1.4\nDamage: 100\n\n 2.3\nAdditional Information\nThe lost blade of the Commander of the Abyss, this edge cuts into an enemy\'s soul.\n\nNotes:\n\nBashes don\'t pierce evasion.\n Abyssal Blade\'s bash does not stack with the bash of  Skull Basher and other Abyssal Blades.\nWhen obtaining multiple items with the bash ability, only the first bought one\'s bash works while the others are disabled.');
